caption.body: Be inspired by four short documentary videos featured online, each with stories of dreamers who take action to positively impact our world. From one man’s dream to build community through roller skating to a band of runners taking action to protect a sacred public land from the threat of development, and from a community of activists creatively confronting one of the planet’s greatest environmental challenges to a rising literary star intent on sharing his inspiration with those who may need it most.  Our screening room may still be closed, but you can watch the videos online at: http://bit.ly/VideoArts <--or navigate here via the link in our bio.
